data.description: We want to welcome you to this one story attached townhome located in Timberlane Village. This property features a long driveway for at least four vehicles and covered front patio.  As you enter you will find an U-shaped kitchen with lots of cabinets, open to the breakfast nook that spills into the living room with cathedral ceiling featuring a woodburning fireplace and windows overlooking the large fenced yard.  There are 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths.  The primary suite towards the front of the property is spacious with the walk in closet and large bath.  May qualify for Rural Development Loan, please check with lender.  Seller willing to assist with closing costs but will be rolled into price.
